🔟 Full Flow Summary
Step 1:

User hits /saml/login

Step 2:

Rails builds SAML AuthRequest → redirects to ADFS

Step 3:

User logs in at ADFS

Step 4:

ADFS sends signed SAMLResponse to /saml/consume

Step 5:

Rails verifies signature using ADFS public certificate

Step 6:

Extract attributes

Step 7:

Map groups → roles

Step 8:

Login user



